column4: NSLOCTEXT("[D9D88FEF47805579586662865563DC56]", "F37828874FD3E3C40E79CBB7794F76FE", "What do you mean? Why are you here?")
NSLOCTEXT("[D9D88FEF47805579586662865563DC56]", "A793CD364F5328A69BC27F9C9B41C255", "When I tried to make my own harem in the city, I was kicked out!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D9D88FEF47805579586662865563DC56]", "1BF1D39B4EED9F6A6B1AFA9D381017FA", "I hear you\'re doing real good these days. I\'ll sell you something good!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D9D88FEF47805579586662865563DC56]", "B7A031624ABADBCCD393C1BF15A8AFBE", "That\'ll be fifty thous bits. No loans, please.")
